                            "<td id='vote'>"+get_candidate_votes(races[i]).join("<br />")+"</td>"+
                            "<td id='vote_percent'>"+get_candidate_percent(races[i]).join("<br />")+"</td>"+
                            "<td id='call_status'>"+get_race_status(races[i])+"</td>"+
                            "<td id='call_at'>"+((typeof(races[i].call_at) != "undefined") ? races[i].call_at : "") +"</td>"+
                            "<td id='call_lead'>"+((typeof(races[i].call_lead) != "undefined") ? races[i].call_lead : "")+"</td>"+
                            "<td id='lead_party'>"+getPartyLead(races[i])+"</td>"+
                        "</tr>");

                }

                init_tablesorter();
                global_after = json.updated
                long_poll_editorial();

            })

        }
```

after it builds the table, it initalizes tablesorter.

